flowchart TD
    A[UI caller\ntrigger: App.handleRun\nfile: src/frontend/src/App.tsx] -->|RuntimeAgentRunRequest {query, optional thread/checkpoint}| B[streamAgentRun\nfile: src/frontend/src/utils/stream.ts\nfunction: streamAgentRun]
    B -->|POST /api/agents/run/stream\nwhy: receive heartbeat/progress before final answer| C[Backend SSE route\nfile: src/backend/routers/agent.py\nfunction: runtime_agent_run_stream]
    C -->|SSE data frames\nRuntimeAgentStreamEvent JSON| D[consumeSseFrames + parseSseDataFrame\nfile: src/frontend/src/utils/stream.ts]
    D -->|validate shape| E[isRuntimeAgentStreamEvent\nfile: src/frontend/src/lib/stream-events.ts]
    E -->|ordered events| F{Ordering checks\nheartbeat first\nstrictly increasing sequence\nsub_queries before completed}
    F -->|valid| G[onEvent callback\nwhy: update UI incrementally]
    F -->|valid completed| H[ApiResult ok\n{events, completed}]
    F -->|invalid shape/order| I[ApiResult error\nmalformed_response\nretryable=false]
    D -->|stream ends without completed| J[ApiResult error\nnetwork interrupted\nretryable=true]

    K[Tradeoff: strict event ordering\nDecision in streamAgentRun\nRejects out-of-contract streams early] -.-> F
    L[Tradeoff: fetch+ReadableStream over EventSource\nDecision in streamAgentRun\nSupports POST payload + deterministic parser tests] -.-> D
